$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,wo,op.On top of the hill... Up higher.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ka,fr,op.Come on Bradley. You walk too slow.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.Keep loosening the dirt. I will find a tarp or sheet for you to pile it onto.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,ex.I’ve got a big blanket we can pile the dirt onto. Be sure there is enough to fill the hole.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ba,ex.Actually, we would need to subtract the volume of Tillman’s body from the pile.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,op.Well... Do that math while you dig.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.Sorry, but there is only one pickaxe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.Sorry, but there is only one pickaxe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,an,ex.Brad. I finished collecting the dirt, but Simon is taking too long.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.Ok I’ll see if I can help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ba,ex.It was buried in the ground. It’s some sort of metal part.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,fr,op.The trap is set! It’s just a matter of time now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,ba,ex.It’s getting late. If Tillman is returning here we’ll be ready.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Pa,ba,op.Go back Buddie. Your work is done.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,wo,op.Just like that? What about Violet? Where is she?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Pa,ba,ex.She is safe with me my Son. Our Violet is not safe with the others.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,op.She’s alone in the dark woods. How is she safe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,op.No Father. But for my peace of mind. I must know that she is not alone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Pa,ba,op.I am with her in a safe place. But I must return to her, my body is failing me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Pa,ba,op.Yes my Son. My moments are numbered, but through the grace of God I will stay alive as long as Violet needs my protection.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.I don’t understand what’s going on. You’ve treated the girls for months and yet they make no progress. I don’t mean to question you, but perhaps the curse is too powerful for you to take on yourself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Pa,ba,op.Don’t worry my Son. It’s almost over. I only have one final request.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Pa,ba,op.If I am to expire I will use my final breath to bring you to Violet. But if I do, you must keep the men away from Violet until she gives birth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,wo,op.What do you mean? I don’t understand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Pa,ba,ex.I’m sorry I have not been more forward with you Buddie. But please trust me. My strength is failing and I must return.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,sh,op.Brad! What the hell are you doing out here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Uhhh... It’s Mendel. He’s gone insane and is burying Denny’s body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,op.Stay clear of Mendel. I’ll deal with him later.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.What do you think Parker did with her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,cl.I don’t know... I don’t know what he’s up to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Well, which way are you going to go? You have no idea where Parker could be going?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,op.I’ll figure it out... I just need to stop and think.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.But if you run across any clues. Let me know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.If you run across any clues to help find Violet let me know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,op.I don’t know. But the old church used to be over there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.I thought the old church was part of the seminary building.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.No Brad... I mean the original church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.Do you think there is shelter over there for Violet?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,ex.Keep looking out here Mendel. I’m sure you’ll find Elizabeth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,wo,op.It’s so dark. I can’t see a thing.");
